<Body> 
	<Title>长江大桥昨晚一桥洞失火 火灾持续1个多小时</Title>  
	<ReportTime type="absTime">2009-08-05</ReportTime>  
	<Content>　 
		<Paragraph> 
			<Sentence> 
				<Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e1"> 
					<Participant sid="s1">新华报业网</Participant>  
					<Denoter did="d1" type="statement">讯</Denoter> 
				</Event>  
				<Event eid="e2"> 
					<Time type="relTime" tid="t2">昨晚</Time> ， 
					<Location lid="l2">南京长江大桥回龙桥一桥洞</Location>  
					<Denoter type="emergency" did="d2">失火</Denoter> 
				</Event> ， 
				<Event eid="e3"> 
					<Denoter type="emergency" did="d3">火灾</Denoter> 持续了 
					<Time type="timeInterval" tid="t3">1个多小时</Time> 
				</Event> ，因为失火桥洞“悬”在河面上，消防人员很难进入施救。
			</Sentence>  
			<Sentence> 
				<Event eid="e4">最后 
					<Participant sid="s4">两名消防队员</Participant> 用 
					<Object type="tool" oid="o4">绳子</Object>  
					<Denoter type="action" did="d4">系</Denoter> 在 
					<Location lid="l4">腰上</Location> 
				</Event> ， 
				<Event eid="e5">从 
					<Location type="origin" lid="l5">桥面上空</Location>  
					<Denoter type="movement" did="d5">降</Denoter> 到 
					<Location type="destination" lid="l5">半空</Location> 
				</Event> ， 
				<Event eid="e6">花了 
					<Time type="timeInterval" tid="t6">近半个小时</Time> 终于把 
					<Object oid="o6">火</Object>  
					<Denoter type="stateChange" did="d6">扑灭</Denoter> 
				</Event> 。
			</Sentence>  
			<Sentence>据了解，火灾因堆放在桥洞里的垃圾引起。</Sentence> 
		</Paragraph>  
		<Paragraph> 
			<Sentence> 
				<Event eid="e7"> 
					<Denoter type="action" did="d7">接到</Denoter>  
					<Object oid="o7">报料</Object> 
				</Event> 后 
				<Event eid="e8"> 
					<Participant sid="s8">记者</Participant> 立刻 
					<Denoter type="movement" did="d8">赶到</Denoter> 了 
					<Location lid="l8">现场</Location> 
				</Event> ， 
				<Event eid="e9"> 
					<Denoter type="emergency" did="d9">失火</Denoter> 地点在 
					<Location lid="l9">南京长江大桥回龙桥上桥口，金川河的出江口处</Location> 
				</Event> 。
			</Sentence>  
			<Sentence> 
				<Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e10"> 
					<Participant sid="s10">记者</Participant> 只能在 
					<Location lid="l10">距离150米远的地方</Location>  
					<Denoter type="perception" did="d10">观看</Denoter> 
				</Event> 。
			</Sentence>  
			<Sentence>在金川河正上方的桥洞里面火光熊熊，空气中弥漫着布料和电线燃烧后的焦糊味。</Sentence>  
			<Sentence> 
				<Event eid="e11"> 
					<Participant sid="s11">消防人员</Participant> 已 
					<Denoter type="movement" did="d11">赶到</Denoter> 了 
					<Location type="destination" lid="l11">桥面</Location> ，
				</Event> 但因为桥洞是悬在半空的，普通的方法根本不能靠近桥洞。
			</Sentence> 
		</Paragraph>  
		<Paragraph> 
			<Sentence> 
				<Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e12"> 
					<Time type="relTime" tid="t12">不久</Time>  
					<Participant sid="s12">记者</Participant>  
					<Denoter type="perception" did="d12">看到</Denoter> 惊险的 
					<Object oid="o12">一幕</Object> 
				</Event> ， 
				<Event eid="e13"> 
					<Participant sid="s13">两名消防人员</Participant>  
					<Location lid="l13">腰间</Location>  
					<Denoter type="action" did="d13">系</Denoter> 着 
					<Object oid="o13">绳子</Object> 
				</Event> ， 
				<Event eid="e14">从 
					<Location type="origin" lid="l14">桥面上</Location> 慢慢 
					<Denoter type="movement" did="d14">空降</Denoter> 到 
					<Location type="destination" lid="l14">桥洞前方</Location> 
				</Event> ， 
				<Event eid="e15">然后用 
					<Object type="tool" oid="o15">水枪</Object>  
					<Denoter type="operation" did="d15">灭火</Denoter> 
				</Event> ，随着水不断地冲击桥洞， 
				<Event eid="e16"> 
					<Participant sid="s16">记者</Participant>  
					<Denoter type="perception" did="d16">听</Denoter>到了
					<Object oid="o16">“噼里啪啦”声</Object>
				</Event>，应该是灼热的水泥被水冲击后发生了爆裂。
			</Sentence>  
			<Sentence>
				<Event eid="e17">
					<Time type="relTime" tid="t17">大约半小时后</Time>，
					<Object oid="o17">火</Object>被
					<Denoter type="stateChange" did="d17">扑灭</Denoter>
				</Event>。
			</Sentence>
		</Paragraph> 
	</Content>  
